==English==

===Etymology===
* (''adverb, adjective'') ''[[a-]]'' + ''[[gape]]''.
* (''noun'') From [[Greek]] ''[[ag치p캡]]'' (love).

===Pronunciation===
*(''adverb, adjective''):
**{{AHD|톛g캐p췂}}, {{IPA|/톛틛토e톩p/}}, {{SAMPA|/@"geIp/}}
**{{audio|en-us-agape.ogg|Audio (US), adverb/adjective}}
*(''noun''):
**{{AHD|칛g칛췂p캐}}, {{IPA|/톔틣틛토톔틣pe톩/}}, {{SAMPA|/A:"gA:peI/}}, ''or'' {{AHD|칛췂g톛p캐}}, {{IPA|/틛톔틣토톛pe톩/}}, {{SAMPA|/"A:g@peI/}}
